high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to reach the countertop to the left of the sink.
Pick up the rightmost bottle of lotion from the countertop.
Turn to face the drawers under the sink.
Put the bottle of lotion in lowest, third drawer to the right under the sink countertop.
Turn to face the sink countertop.
Pick up the other bottle of lotion from the sink countertop.
Turn to face the drawers under the sink.
Put the other bottle of lotion in lowest, third drawer to the right under the sink countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of lotion away under the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the wall, then turn right and go forward to the counter.
Pick up the rightmost soap bottle on the counter.
Turn around and move forward, then turn back around to face the counter.
Open the bottom drawer beneath the counter, third to the right, and put the soap bottle in it.
Look back up at the counter.
Pick up the remaining soap bottle on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and move forward, then turn back around to face the counter.
Open the bottom drawer beneath the counter, third to the right, and put the soap bottle in it.
anns.task_desc: Put two soap bottles in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right the head to the sink counter
Pick up the container on your right at the counter
Turn around then adjust your position facing the sink drawer on the right
Put the container in the drawer then close it
Move closer to the  counter
Pick up the other container
Turn around adjust your position facing the sink drawer
Put the container in the drawer then close it
anns.task_desc: Put two containers in the drawer
